Privacy Policy
This document describes the data collected by the mobile application Coton.
The information we receive
The application collects the following information anonymously: number, date and frequency of uses, activity within the application (pages displayed, duration, external links visited), operating system, IP address.
The application does not have access to the following information: last name and first name, e-mail address, telephone number or any other personally identifiable information.
How we use this information
This information allows us to analyze the use that is made of the application, to improve it and to detect possible problems of operation.
We do not use this information to track individual usage of the application, but to identify trends across all users.
We reserve the right to share aggregated statistics (but never raw data) with some of our partners.
